      </div>
      <div class="hard"></div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text">I Am a Cimarrón</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Let everything around us tremble—<br>because I love freedom.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I live in these times,<br>and I think of what our ancestors suffered,<br>fighting for a better life,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">far from the whip<br>and other abuse.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I speak for those who could not voice their sorrow,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and for those who shook off their slavery—<br>those who came from Africa<br>but were never slaves in spirit.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">I love the freedom of thought,<br>of belief, of religion—<br>we were born free.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Society molds us to its liking,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">we must be strong,<br>accurate, incredible, and grounded.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Do the impossible to find<br>our reason for being,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">connect to the energy of the universe,<br>and discover our potential.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Keep the dagger hidden,<br>without harming even the petal of a flower.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Add clouds to love,<br>take part in its rain,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">make the existence of a higher being your own.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Pray to our gods,<br>without posing.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Humbly listen to an elder,<br>help a blind man,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">overcome your reflection<br>in the clearest water,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">visit Olympia in dreams,<br>go to an old shrine,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">give your life daily<br>so we don’t fall asleep on the path,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and defend our destiny—<br>if it’s for the good, of course.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Live without a budget, each day nonstop.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Create, and let the deepest wounds heal.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Love your chosen one,<br>climb an avenue,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and enjoy the process:</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">always add, never subtract,<br>multiply to infinity.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Make real the myth<br>of those who refused to live in slavery,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">making it possible<br>to free the soul,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">to refresh it in times like these.</p>
      </div>

